      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "A Frosty Stalemate",
        "Client": "Returning Villager",
        "Description": "Hey, um, sorry to interrupt you, but\r\nI think there\u0027s something out in the\r\nFrost Islands that \u0022may\u0022 need your\r\nattention. These two monsters have\r\nbeen going at it for a while now and\r\nit seems to be getting worse. Just,\r\nuh, thought you should know.",
        "Target": "Hunt a Goss Harag and a Tetranadon",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Status quo glac\u00E9",
        "Client": "Villageois qui revient",
        "Description": "H\u00E9... Euh... D\u00E9sol\u00E9 de te d\u00E9ranger,\r\nmais il faudrait peut-\u00EAtre que\r\ntu ailles jeter un \u0153il \u00E0 l\u0027Archipel\r\nde glace. Ces deux monstres\r\nn\u0027arr\u00EAtent pas de s\u0027y battre, et \u00E7a\r\ndevient de pire en pire. Enfin bon,\r\nje dis \u00E7a comme \u00E7a, hein.",
        "Target": "Chasser un Goss Harag et un Tetranadon",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Stallo pericoloso",
        "Client": "Abitante di ritorno",
        "Description": "Non vorrei disturbare, ma c\u0027\u00E8\r\nqualcosa che necessita della\r\ntua attenzione alle Isole\r\nghiacciate. Due mostri se le\r\ndanno da un po\u0027 e la situazione\r\nsta peggiorando. Credevo fosse\r\ngiusto fartelo sapere...",
        "Target": "Caccia un Goss Harag e un Tetranadon",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Ein frostiges Patt",
        "Client": "Heimkehrender D\u00F6rfler",
        "Description": "Hey, \u00E4hm, entschuldige die St\u00F6rung,\r\naber auf den Frostinseln gibt es was,\r\ndas deine Aufmerksamkeit vertragen\r\n\u0022k\u00F6nnte\u0022. Die beiden Monster beharken\r\nsich schon eine ganze Weile und es\r\nscheint schlimmer zu werden. Dachte\r\nnur, du, \u00E4h, solltest das wissen.",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Goss Harag und\r\neinen Tetranadon.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Tablas escarchadas",
        "Client": "Viajero de regreso",
        "Description": "Hay dos monstruos enormes\r\nli\u00E1ndola parda en las Islas\r\nheladas. A\u00FAn no han herido a\r\nnadie, pero es cuesti\u00F3n de\r\ntiempo. Alguien tiene que\r\ncazarlos. Y ese alguien...\r\npodr\u00EDas ser t\u00FA, \u00BFno?",
        "Target": "Caza un Goss Harag y un Tetranadon",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0425\u043E\u043B\u043E\u0434\u043D\u044B\u0439 \u0442\u0443\u043F\u0438\u043A",
        "Client": "\u0412\u043E\u0437\u0432\u0440\u0430\u0449\u0430\u044E\u0449\u0438\u0439\u0441\u044F \u0436\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043B\u044C",
